    "body": "SOLVED\n\nNeed to subscribe to app::window-all-closed event as default behaviour is to quit app when all windows are closed otherwise.\n\nhttps://github.com/electron/electron/blob/master/docs/api/app.md#event-window-all-closed\n\nLooks like this behaviour was only described in mid May.\n\nWeirdly in my googling couldn't find any use of this in simple examples around app lifetime.\n"
